oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mac Wiseman at Earl's Drive In
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Wiseman, Mac; Boys from Indiana (Musical group); Metal photoplates; Ramblin' Lou Family Band;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on light blue) announcing Mac Wiseman, the Boys From Indiana with Ramblin' Lou's Family Band featuring Linda Lou at Earl's Drive In on June 27. Poster features metal photoplate of Mac Wiseman, the Boys From Indiana, and Linda Lou.
